{"tid":1898552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 呢八個月來韓國人咁撐我地 可以點幫返佢地？","createTime":"2020-02-26T06:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T06:07:59.000Z","uid":81268,"like":44,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"53a339f735044243b27eff778a5fcb8629e7a275","tid":1898552,"uid":81268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"今日韓國感染人數已經破千，社區傳播已經失控，港共直頭對韓國封埋關。成個反送中以來韓國人一直咁撐我哋，而家係時候做啲嘢幫返人地<br />\n<br />\n文在寅政府奶共係一回事，但韓國平民都係中共肺炎受害者，而家疫情失控程度僅次於中國，韓國人反中情緒已經空前高漲，之前仲有聯署要求禁止中國人入境，係反共立場上都係手足來<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出錢出力寄物資傳資訊乜都好，我哋應該諗下點樣幫返佢哋</strong></span> </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國人準備爆 大規模排斥同趕絕緊支那人 50萬人請願要求封關<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qeX0BQy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqeX0BQy.jpg&h=6f66e05b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1875244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1875244</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國人近代史上一直處於民主抗爭嘅前線，先後經歷過1980光州運動、1987六月運動、2016反朴槿惠示威，普遍都好明白香港人嘅處境。我地走緊嘅路，佢地一早已經走過，係追求民主上算係前輩，成場反送中革命以來韓國主流民意都企係我地呢邊，一直不遺餘力咁撐我地撐到出晒面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港嘅情況一直都係韓國新聞嘅焦點，有乜風吹草動嘢嘢都上到人地 top news，自舊年6月起已經一直派記者來到香港前線，KBS亦整咗訪問港警同有關香港人被殺嘅專輯節目<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">真。核彈 KBS時事直擊核彈終結</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717826</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國KBS訪問 香港被自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hSz6piM3IIw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhSz6piM3IIw&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=5e709be2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hSz6piM3IIw</a><br />\n<br />\n時事追擊 - 香港被自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/brB0YUvFnKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbrB0YUvFnKI&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=06978e43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/brB0YUvFnKI</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">演員金義聖一直身體力行支持香港，大家都好清楚，除咗發起 #Eye4HK 行動，早幾個月仲直頭飛來香港上埋前線</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/2fDxqx7.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/LbJmint.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">金義聖《Straight》報導香港抗爭</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590383</a><br />\n<br />\n探查企劃Straight《香港的憤怒&mdash;金義聖》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/I3UT2qEc_LE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FI3UT2qEc_LE&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=76e138a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/I3UT2qEc_LE</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>真係希望有朝一日金義聖先生可以參演香港嘅電影，光復成功之後一定要邀請佢來，未演出電影前都起碼要去煲底相擁下先</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">韓國大學生撐香港，撐到同中國留學生開片，然後去中國領事館示威</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.v.daum.net/v/20191118203013850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.v.daum.net%2Fv%2F20191118203013850&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=4a125d3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.v.daum.net/v/20191118203013850</a><br />\n<br />\n成日係明洞舉辦遊行集會聲援香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N7oGk5u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN7oGk5u.jpg&h=a932e725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B6DzMOpFe-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6DzMOpFe-M&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=a456ba04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6DzMOpFe-M&h=0401adeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B6DzMOpFe-M</a><br />\n<br />\n首爾大學生「沉默遊行」聲援香港 抗議南韓政府未有發聲撐港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/NR5f7gm.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/swNFyWm.jpg\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191112/60257777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257777&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=64a70885\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257777&h=72aa5498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191112/60257777</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國校園裏的香港話題：本地學生捲入衝突和中國留學生對峙<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/uvd9sib.jpg\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50449660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50449660&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=2e3186fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50449660&h=a2c5175b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50449660</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港警攻打 CU 同 Poly 校園，亦深深引起韓國人對學運嘅共鳴，喚醒當地學運曾被血腥鎮壓嘅記憶，將中大理大戰役同延世大學比較</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/usppf9H.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/rQDxp22.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n有手足係弘大搞反送中展覽，勁多當地人去捧場，留低大量打氣字句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/6zDEPDT.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j42jR8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj42jR8c.jpg&h=f0919313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwB43eS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwB43eS.jpg&h=eaab3fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B44gAXzBted/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB44gAXzBted%2F&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=3dd9a904\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB44gAXzBted%2F&h=8fc8bf50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B44gAXzBted/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>韓國人真係一直 Stand with Hong Kong，咁我地可以點樣報答人地？</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 雖然我地仲係自身難保，但都盡量幫韓國人渡過疫情難關<br />\n2. 以後多啲去韓國旅行<br />\n3. 多啲支持韓國產品，進口韓國貨，將黃色經濟圈擴大至貿易層面，建立黃色貿易圈<br />\n4. 黃店可以考慮俾優惠/特別待遇韓國遊客<br />\n5. 將來多啲學術交流同合作，尤其是科研技術方面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>韓國人 we connect 到如此程度，我地都應該係時候幫返人地，唔可以忘恩負義</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nStand with Hong Kong<br />\nStand with Korea<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/zKgK0LH.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"749f6f47ef6360a7d3374e3f57b9325a52aa1903","tid":1898552,"uid":84064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:14:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85589f09e0703a2fe6553e9ff1774470bd38bb4a","tid":1898552,"uid":121995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:16:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fe63d4d451a4b8857b2b488ae7fadccce9db778","tid":1898552,"uid":121995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:17:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1465ee73488df497aafb93977c05da89f7768af7","tid":1898552,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:18:53.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n暫時可以做真係得進口韓貨，幫趁韓店自己都冇口罩，捐唔到俾佢哋。"},{"pid":"44ab24ae52fcc3dd50c14ddc51e949e1d05a6daf","tid":1898552,"uid":311328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:19:15.000Z","msg":"起碼幫佢地打打氣先 入面有絲打幫手翻譯你嘅信息做韓文 然後自己放上Twitter 俾佢地知道香港人都支持佢地 <br />\n<br />\n終於有機會同韓國手足講聲加油<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1897111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1897111</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f7d2b5921ac102f1081ab2bb411ddd3345bb364c","tid":1898552,"uid":290640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:19:22.000Z","msg":"支持 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8003337a173f8bbe294d7d00d595603e1690df4","tid":1898552,"uid":271530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53a339f735044243b27eff778a5fcb8629e7a275","tid":1898552,"uid":81268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"今日韓國感染人數已經破千，社區傳播已經失控，港共直頭對韓國封埋關。成個反送中以來韓國人一直咁撐我哋，而家係時候做啲嘢幫返人地<br />\n<br />\n文在寅政府奶共係一回事，但韓國平民都係中共肺炎受害者，而家疫情失控程度僅次於中國，韓國人反中情緒已經空前高漲，之前仲有聯署要求禁止中國人入境，係反共立場上都係手足來<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出錢出力寄物資傳資訊乜都好，我哋應該諗下點樣幫返佢哋</strong></span> </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國人準備爆 大規模排斥同趕絕緊支那人 50萬人請願要求封關<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qeX0BQy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqeX0BQy.jpg&h=6f66e05b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1875244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1875244</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國人近代史上一直處於民主抗爭嘅前線，先後經歷過1980光州運動、1987六月運動、2016反朴槿惠示威，普遍都好明白香港人嘅處境。我地走緊嘅路，佢地一早已經走過，係追求民主上算係前輩，成場反送中革命以來韓國主流民意都企係我地呢邊，一直不遺餘力咁撐我地撐到出晒面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港嘅情況一直都係韓國新聞嘅焦點，有乜風吹草動嘢嘢都上到人地 top news，自舊年6月起已經一直派記者來到香港前線，KBS亦整咗訪問港警同有關香港人被殺嘅專輯節目<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">真。核彈 KBS時事直擊核彈終結</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717826</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國KBS訪問 香港被自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hSz6piM3IIw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhSz6piM3IIw&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=5e709be2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hSz6piM3IIw</a><br />\n<br />\n時事追擊 - 香港被自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/brB0YUvFnKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbrB0YUvFnKI&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=06978e43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/brB0YUvFnKI</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">演員金義聖一直身體力行支持香港，大家都好清楚，除咗發起 #Eye4HK 行動，早幾個月仲直頭飛來香港上埋前線</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/2fDxqx7.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/LbJmint.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">金義聖《Straight》報導香港抗爭</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590383</a><br />\n<br />\n探查企劃Straight《香港的憤怒&mdash;金義聖》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/I3UT2qEc_LE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FI3UT2qEc_LE&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=76e138a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/I3UT2qEc_LE</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>真係希望有朝一日金義聖先生可以參演香港嘅電影，光復成功之後一定要邀請佢來，未演出電影前都起碼要去煲底相擁下先</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">韓國大學生撐香港，撐到同中國留學生開片，然後去中國領事館示威</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.v.daum.net/v/20191118203013850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.v.daum.net%2Fv%2F20191118203013850&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=4a125d3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.v.daum.net/v/20191118203013850</a><br />\n<br />\n成日係明洞舉辦遊行集會聲援香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N7oGk5u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN7oGk5u.jpg&h=a932e725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B6DzMOpFe-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6DzMOpFe-M&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=a456ba04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6DzMOpFe-M&h=0401adeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B6DzMOpFe-M</a><br />\n<br />\n首爾大學生「沉默遊行」聲援香港 抗議南韓政府未有發聲撐港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/NR5f7gm.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/swNFyWm.jpg\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191112/60257777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257777&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=64a70885\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257777&h=72aa5498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191112/60257777</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國校園裏的香港話題：本地學生捲入衝突和中國留學生對峙<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/uvd9sib.jpg\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50449660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50449660&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=2e3186fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50449660&h=a2c5175b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50449660</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港警攻打 CU 同 Poly 校園，亦深深引起韓國人對學運嘅共鳴，喚醒當地學運曾被血腥鎮壓嘅記憶，將中大理大戰役同延世大學比較</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/usppf9H.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/rQDxp22.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n有手足係弘大搞反送中展覽，勁多當地人去捧場，留低大量打氣字句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/6zDEPDT.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j42jR8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj42jR8c.jpg&h=f0919313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwB43eS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwB43eS.jpg&h=eaab3fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B44gAXzBted/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB44gAXzBted%2F&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=3dd9a904\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB44gAXzBted%2F&h=8fc8bf50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B44gAXzBted/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>韓國人真係一直 Stand with Hong Kong，咁我地可以點樣報答人地？</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 雖然我地仲係自身難保，但都盡量幫韓國人渡過疫情難關<br />\n2. 以後多啲去韓國旅行<br />\n3. 多啲支持韓國產品，進口韓國貨，將黃色經濟圈擴大至貿易層面，建立黃色貿易圈<br />\n4. 黃店可以考慮俾優惠/特別待遇韓國遊客<br />\n5. 將來多啲學術交流同合作，尤其是科研技術方面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>韓國人 we connect 到如此程度，我地都應該係時候幫返人地，唔可以忘恩負義</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nStand with Hong Kong<br />\nStand with Korea<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/zKgK0LH.jpg\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:19:28.000Z","msg":"true"},{"pid":"db3e9f571c03bcdfc4b3fbbfb5848fe6c7dae82f","tid":1898552,"uid":269096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:23:03.000Z","msg":"唔知鍾樂偉會唔會可以幫手諗下，佢係韓國都識咁多人，至少比較快可以知道佢地需要乜，同埋可以點做"},{"pid":"a1903378da2ba0a1cbb72d674e8320483ebf1813","tid":1898552,"uid":43062,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:26:51.000Z","msg":"昨日有Twitter 聲援佢地，但係全世界都唔夠口罩可以點分到比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且有唔少KF98個啲都係韓國黎"},{"pid":"a4f123478fc1c66eff67ba09e04f165642848d56","tid":1898552,"uid":337826,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"反送中之前好憎韓狗，但真正做到 #standwithhongkong 真係得韓國人<br />\n<br />\n不如集合人手車HK Mask 之後連 filter送過去"},{"pid":"78648cb2fcad5fef4099f46fd1ce3a323757faac","tid":1898552,"uid":311328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:04:03.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫手推下啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a68bb647854a640284a050335a6a33cf0fe6f36","tid":1898552,"uid":81268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:19:43.000Z","msg":"有冇身處韓國嘅手足可以講下而家嗰邊缺唔缺口罩同其他消毒用品？"},{"pid":"399f4af0eb391a4c66e9311eacb795838ccd7e1e","tid":1898552,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T10:54:10.000Z","msg":"以香港市民名義拍條南韓加油得唔得?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1897076\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1897076</a>"},{"pid":"3c2adb06800a6c9a281518c265dc23b4eae073eb","tid":1898552,"uid":56829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ee056670a4d79c40bad4eac55e26352d061df3a","tid":1898552,"uid":197716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"e54d6e6bd5dc164f46d5e03802be375173a0ce1f","tid":1898552,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4f123478fc1c66eff67ba09e04f165642848d56","tid":1898552,"uid":337826,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"反送中之前好憎韓狗，但真正做到 #standwithhongkong 真係得韓國人<br />\n<br />\n不如集合人手車HK Mask 之後連 filter送過去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"真係要幫下佢地手，佢地真係幾大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d01037660fa49a65a58bea4cc0e0c6c80b20c6","tid":1898552,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53a339f735044243b27eff778a5fcb8629e7a275","tid":1898552,"uid":81268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"今日韓國感染人數已經破千，社區傳播已經失控，港共直頭對韓國封埋關。成個反送中以來韓國人一直咁撐我哋，而家係時候做啲嘢幫返人地<br />\n<br />\n文在寅政府奶共係一回事，但韓國平民都係中共肺炎受害者，而家疫情失控程度僅次於中國，韓國人反中情緒已經空前高漲，之前仲有聯署要求禁止中國人入境，係反共立場上都係手足來<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出錢出力寄物資傳資訊乜都好，我哋應該諗下點樣幫返佢哋</strong></span> </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國人準備爆 大規模排斥同趕絕緊支那人 50萬人請願要求封關<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qeX0BQy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqeX0BQy.jpg&h=6f66e05b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1875244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1875244</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國人近代史上一直處於民主抗爭嘅前線，先後經歷過1980光州運動、1987六月運動、2016反朴槿惠示威，普遍都好明白香港人嘅處境。我地走緊嘅路，佢地一早已經走過，係追求民主上算係前輩，成場反送中革命以來韓國主流民意都企係我地呢邊，一直不遺餘力咁撐我地撐到出晒面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港嘅情況一直都係韓國新聞嘅焦點，有乜風吹草動嘢嘢都上到人地 top news，自舊年6月起已經一直派記者來到香港前線，KBS亦整咗訪問港警同有關香港人被殺嘅專輯節目<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">真。核彈 KBS時事直擊核彈終結</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717826</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國KBS訪問 香港被自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hSz6piM3IIw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhSz6piM3IIw&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=5e709be2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hSz6piM3IIw</a><br />\n<br />\n時事追擊 - 香港被自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/brB0YUvFnKI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbrB0YUvFnKI&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=06978e43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/brB0YUvFnKI</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">演員金義聖一直身體力行支持香港，大家都好清楚，除咗發起 #Eye4HK 行動，早幾個月仲直頭飛來香港上埋前線</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/2fDxqx7.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/LbJmint.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">金義聖《Straight》報導香港抗爭</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590383</a><br />\n<br />\n探查企劃Straight《香港的憤怒&mdash;金義聖》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/I3UT2qEc_LE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FI3UT2qEc_LE&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=76e138a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/I3UT2qEc_LE</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>真係希望有朝一日金義聖先生可以參演香港嘅電影，光復成功之後一定要邀請佢來，未演出電影前都起碼要去煲底相擁下先</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">韓國大學生撐香港，撐到同中國留學生開片，然後去中國領事館示威</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.v.daum.net/v/20191118203013850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.v.daum.net%2Fv%2F20191118203013850&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=4a125d3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.v.daum.net/v/20191118203013850</a><br />\n<br />\n成日係明洞舉辦遊行集會聲援香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N7oGk5u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN7oGk5u.jpg&h=a932e725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B6DzMOpFe-M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6DzMOpFe-M&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=a456ba04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB6DzMOpFe-M&h=0401adeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B6DzMOpFe-M</a><br />\n<br />\n首爾大學生「沉默遊行」聲援香港 抗議南韓政府未有發聲撐港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/NR5f7gm.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/swNFyWm.jpg\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191112/60257777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257777&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=64a70885\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191112%2F60257777&h=72aa5498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191112/60257777</a><br />\n<br />\n韓國校園裏的香港話題：本地學生捲入衝突和中國留學生對峙<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/uvd9sib.jpg\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50449660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50449660&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=2e3186fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-50449660&h=a2c5175b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-50449660</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港警攻打 CU 同 Poly 校園，亦深深引起韓國人對學運嘅共鳴，喚醒當地學運曾被血腥鎮壓嘅記憶，將中大理大戰役同延世大學比較</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/usppf9H.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/rQDxp22.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n有手足係弘大搞反送中展覽，勁多當地人去捧場，留低大量打氣字句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/6zDEPDT.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j42jR8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj42jR8c.jpg&h=f0919313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwB43eS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwB43eS.jpg&h=eaab3fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B44gAXzBted/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB44gAXzBted%2F&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=3dd9a904\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB44gAXzBted%2F&h=8fc8bf50\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B44gAXzBted/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>韓國人真係一直 Stand with Hong Kong，咁我地可以點樣報答人地？</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 雖然我地仲係自身難保，但都盡量幫韓國人渡過疫情難關<br />\n2. 以後多啲去韓國旅行<br />\n3. 多啲支持韓國產品，進口韓國貨，將黃色經濟圈擴大至貿易層面，建立黃色貿易圈<br />\n4. 黃店可以考慮俾優惠/特別待遇韓國遊客<br />\n5. 將來多啲學術交流同合作，尤其是科研技術方面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>韓國人 we connect 到如此程度，我地都應該係時候幫返人地，唔可以忘恩負義</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nStand with Hong Kong<br />\nStand with Korea<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/zKgK0LH.jpg\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:31:58.000Z","msg":"賣返口罩比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68fe672504a25561489af1dc1fa1cf2e68ddfd39","tid":1898552,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:32:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"938bdf94dc2f401d8495661a75bbe502374b9508","tid":1898552,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:32:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3d6b97adc75524f665298e8d6f1040a6b6281df2","tid":1898552,"uid":141645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:40:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f53dda0a9a58ef0163a41d6bb7c546c668b20c0e","tid":1898552,"uid":72065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fe2c300b36f0674ad75890201ffa01cda9f732","tid":1898552,"uid":72065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93308ce7e0786bbab586db0ee2410affdeebf6f","tid":1898552,"uid":47161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T12:42:52.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3167efa9937b8b8bf05f554d46ca27e6147a59ce","tid":1898552,"uid":81268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T21:09:04.000Z","msg":"有冇身處韓國嘅手足？"}]}